                Minuten Schriftführer: <lb xml:id="uuid_69eab84e-fc9f-4825-aab8-4efc9f982568"/>Dr.
                    <rs type="person" ref="#51604">Korst</rs>
                <rs type="person" ref="#55036">Schlöser</rs>.</p>
